{"tid":1987040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冇得沖涼 麥難民減少郁動","createTime":"2020-04-24T08:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:00:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1116e365b2aaf0001c0d4e89026c86f1b4f0d550","tid":1987040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200424/RBOVMLONCOSXU7AJI6GWKXTWPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FRBOVMLONCOSXU7AJI6GWKXTWPQ%2F&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabknwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=b06012a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200424%2FRBOVMLONCOSXU7AJI6GWKXTWPQ%2F&h=967894ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200424/RBOVMLONCOSXU7AJI6GWKXTWPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n冇得沖涼 麥難民減少郁動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200424/large/1587659773_8983.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587659773_8983.jpg&h=68a3c671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿權租住的劏房環境衞生惡劣，鼠輩橫行，因此寧可到麥當勞休息。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞早前一度取消晚市堂食，令一眾麥難民失去容身之所。長駐欽州街麥當勞的阿權，雖月花近2,000元租住20呎劏房，惟劏房衞生惡劣，寧願留宿冷氣開放的麥當勞，由於運動場於疫症下全數關閉，無法洗澡的他，只好以酒精搓手液搽身消毒。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：居病毒溫床 劏房戶：死咗冇人知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200424/large/1587659771_7250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587659771_7250.jpg&h=1c279cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿權只有20呎的單位，就連他亦不敢進入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200424/large/1587659772_1ea5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200424%2Flarge%2F1587659772_1ea5.jpg&h=75ceb91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿蔣每晚提着手提袋及個人物品到快餐店留宿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比尿味悶熱劏房舒適<br />\n<br />\n38歲的阿權當上麥難民兩年，過去曾有一份穩定工作，與父母及胞姐同住，直至父母先後因癌症離世，才搬出獨立生活。但天生濕疹的他，兩年前雙眼不幸患上白內障喪失大部份視力，被迫辭掉倉務員工作，流落街頭。他指為符合申請公屋資格，去年11月起，每月花1,900元，租下一個面積不足20平方呎的劏房。<br />\n<br />\n記者曾到訪阿權位於福榮街的家，劏房位於唐樓的梯間，業主將梯間約3呎闊、6呎長的空位以石屎圍封，在內加設坐廁後出租。劏房內廁所不能沖廁，地面充斥污迹與尿味，木板充當單人床，睡覺時雙腳不能伸直，房內不通風，更有老鼠出沒。阿權坦言，麥當勞的環境遠較居所舒適，無奈成為麥難民。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞關閉晚市堂食14日其間，阿權每天呆坐店外至翌日凌晨4時，待餐廳解封後再入內休息。以往他會到運動場的更衣室洗澡，但運動場在疫情下關閉，他只好花錢到賓館租房沖涼，或盡量減少郁動，避免出汗，並以酒精消毒液塗抹全身和衣服消毒。<br />\n<br />\n麥難民除了無業人士，還包括50多歲的中醫師阿蔣，自前年5月，他用作中醫診所及住所的單位因失修致天花漏水，業主不肯維修下他退租，展開在土瓜灣的麥難民生涯。現時於慈善團體中藥店掛單應診，希望能儲錢再次「上樓」，並在住處設立自家診所。"},{"pid":"9590b60164efa2b435882d2589622d835e73e5ce","tid":1987040,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code> <br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"2f329d69c5e07290409f55eaa7583b605dd1cb59","tid":1987040,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8b5db8c957065c91181d873a8c5847c33fa7c7b3","tid":1987040,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"最自由經濟體系<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d61972e7b00d3291931cd250784c54155189ed","tid":1987040,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"中醫都要做麥難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bf3eb660c71c329f53153d54f892651d49214e","tid":1987040,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9590b60164efa2b435882d2589622d835e73e5ce","tid":1987040,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code> <br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"乜事？"},{"pid":"02e77982de8dc5c1b4caf1b26378835ef9bf2fc9","tid":1987040,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d61972e7b00d3291931cd250784c54155189ed","tid":1987040,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"中醫都要做麥難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"做中醫真係乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab1e7e2e7edf84b5b9ee6ed78ea37005839f7d2","tid":1987040,"uid":207005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14bf3eb660c71c329f53153d54f892651d49214e","tid":1987040,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9590b60164efa2b435882d2589622d835e73e5ce","tid":1987040,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code> <br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"乜事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"呃負皮"}]}